            <title>[LU-11899] Possible resource/memory leaks</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11899</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Check with static checker&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
cppcheck --enable=all --inconclusive --xml-version=2 --force --library=posix,gnu . 2&amp;gt; /tmp/result.xml&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;revealed two possible resource/memory leaks due to improper error handling in&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
